          <a href="https://pan.quark.cn/s/b1dcb05d59cd" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="font-size:0.72em;padding:5px 8px;background:var(--bg);border-radius:5px;color:var(--text-p);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;transition:all 0.12s;" onmouseover="this.style.color='var(--accent)'" onmouseout="this.style.color='var(--text-p)'"><span>📖</span><span style="overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;white-space:nowrap;flex:1;">2026 小升初冲刺卷（语数英）</span><span style="font-size:0.7em;opacity:0.5;">↗</span></a>
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:0.72em;font-weight:600;color:var(--text-m);padding:8px 0 3px;letter-spacing:0.3px;">🖼️ 精选壁纸合集</div>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:3px;">
